<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-polygonoffset.xml">PolygonOffset</db:link> type adds an offset to the fragment depth value prior to depth test and depth write. The offset can be used to avoid z-fighting when rendering polygons with very close depth values such as decals.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="property-documentation">
<db:title>Property Documentation</db:title>
<db:section xml:id="depthSteps-prop">
<db:title>depthSteps : real</db:title>
<db:para>Holds the units that create constant depth offsets. Default value is 0.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="scaleFactor-prop">
<db:title>scaleFactor : real</db:title>
<db:para>Holds the scale factor used to create a variable depth offset for each polygon. Default value is 0.</db:para>
</db:section>
</db:section>
